This Keyword :
--------------
It is a keyword is a reference variable that refers to the current
object


Uses of This Keyword :
---------------------
-> It is used to refer the current class instance variable
-> it is used to invoke the current class methods
-> It is used to invoke the current class constructor :this()
-> This is the first statement in the constructor call
-> This keyword can be used to pass the argument in the method
	-> This case is mainly used in the event handling
-> This can be used to pass the argument in the constructor

-> This keyword can be used to return the current class instance